{"tid":2511383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度疫情｜民眾一篋篋現金買黑市藥 孟買接種中心因疫苗不夠關門3天","createTime":"2021-05-01T01:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T01:04:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a31d862e6e47401d546b228cd7bd850b3f8b287","tid":2511383,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T01:04:43.000Z","msg":"印度疫情連日大爆發，氧氣等醫療物資嚴重不足。孟買市政府宣佈由於疫苗供應短缺，全市疫苗接種中心周五起關閉3天，當局會在疫苗供應恢復後通知已預約人士。多款藥物供應同樣嚴重不足，更出現黑市炒賣，被視為有助治療COVID-19的抗病毒藥瑞德西韋（Remdesivir）炒價動輒達1,000美元（約7,800港元）一劑，較正常高20倍。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210501/PW5BWZSEKFHPTPKCOFVPHY7B3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210501%2FPW5BWZSEKFHPTPKCOFVPHY7B3I%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=c5ff914d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210501%2FPW5BWZSEKFHPTPKCOFVPHY7B3I%2F&h=a5a43ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210501/PW5BWZSEKFHPTPKCOFVPHY7B3I/</a>"}]}